list.title: Covid: US backs waiver on vaccine patents to boost supply
list.description: The US supports a move to suspend intellectual property protection for Covid-19 vaccines - but not all countries are on board.
list.content:
The US has thrown its support behind a move at the World Trade Organization (WTO) to temporarily lift patent protection for coronavirus vaccines.
